name: Women's Minmatar Republic Officer Jacket
description: The Minmatar Republic's military hierarchy has many officers acutely conscious of status within their circles and tribes, and it is not uncommon to encounter command level officers wearing very nicely tailored uniform jackets. Minmatar fashions fluctuate but an appreciation for earthy tones, patterned fabrics, and elegant cut and trim is unlikely to ever go out of style.
